title: Part 2: Gina Carano (ACS July 7)
itunes:title: Part 2: Gina Carano (ACS July 7)
description:
Actress and former MMA fighter, Gina Carano, joins Adam for a one-on-one interview to talk about her new movie, ‘Terror on the Prairie’. She tells the story of how her Hollywood cancellation halted her career when she was taken off ‘The Mandalorian’ and all other ‘Star Wars’ projects. She recounts the abuse and struggles she faced including how she was tracked with a hashtag, dropped by her talent agency, and labeled a Nazi by former Senator Heidi Heitkamp.
